title: #92Noon Nordo In For PA! Burns/Krawczynski/Leber/Allen
description: PA is in Seattle which means Nordo is in the big chair! Ryan Burns is in studio to talk Gopher football, Jon Krawczynski talks Gophers and Vikings, Ben Leber calls in from Seattle to preview tonight's match up, and Paul Allen joins the show to talk about Week 13!
